                  </hi>. I am a labourer, and live in May's-buildings On the 31st of January I was in William-street, and saw the prisoner in Bedford's custody—I went back with him and got over the fence—I found four shillings—I brought them back to Mr. Cowell's.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18370227-name-366" type="witnessName">
