                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable B</hi> 24.) I was on duty, and met the pri<lb></lb>soner coming back towards Mr. Cowell's shop, in custody of Mr. Cowll's man—I took him to the shop—Mr. Cowell gave me one shilling and then eleven others—the one shilling is marked, the others are not—nothing was found on him.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
